        <h1>About <span class="gradient-text">Satasat</span></h1>
        <p class="about-lead">A peer-to-peer skill barter platform built for CS5054NT Advanced Programming & Technologies at Itahari International College, London Metropolitan University.</p>
        <p>Satasat enables users to exchange skills directly — no money involved. Trade guitar lessons for Nepali language, Python programming for yoga, or any skill you possess for one you want to learn.</p>
